    <h2 class="text-center">About ESABOL Healthy Living Services</h2>
    <div class="col-sm-3">
      <blockquote>
        <p class="text-justify quotes">Beloved, I wish above all things that thou mayest prosper and be in health,
          even as thy soul prospereth.</p>
        <footer class="text-right">
          God<br>
          <cite title="Source Title">3 John 1:2</cite>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>
      <hr>
      <blockquote>
        <p class="text-justify quotes">Health is the greatest form of wealth, and right feeding is one the greatest factors of health.
