    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <h3>How EHLS Started</h3>
      <p id="about" class="text-justify">
        There were just a few juicers. Various home-made juices would be enjoyed by many people, even without knowledge of the Health
        benefits. Along the line, research was made into the health benefits of some of these fruit juices, which you can find on
        our <%= link_to 'blog', blog_path %>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-justify">
        Thus, ESABOL Healthy Living Services was founded in 2009 by Professor Esan A. Aderinola, to the Glory of God, and for the benefit
        of mankind. Since then, ESABOL has grown from a family business into a large business, providing healthy living services, selling
        fresh fruit juices, and servicing events within and outside the home state - Ondo State, Nigeria.
      </p>

      <h3>What we do at EHLS</h3>
      <p class="text-justify">
        We provide fresh fruit juices, including Carrot, Cucumber, Watermelon, Orange, Shaddock, Grape, Pineapple and
        Cabbage juices; Smoothies and Fruit Salad.
        <bold>Our Products are 100% natural (no preservatives), undiluted and without sweeteners.</bold>
      </p>
      <p class="text-justify">
        We can also produce and serve on the spot at your parties and ceremonies. On your call, we can also deliver our products at your
        door step or offices. They are not only therapeutic, they are rejuvenating and reinvigorating. Remember:
        <p class="text-center"><em>"You are what you eat and drink"</em></p>
      </p>
      <br>
      <div class="text-center">
        <%= image_tag 'about-page-picture-1.jpg', class: "img img-responsive img-rounded img-thumbnail about-image" %>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center"><em>ESABOL orange juice, watermelon juice, carrot juice and fruit salad.</em></p>
      <br>
      <p class="text-justify">
        EHLS is not primarily a profit-making organization. We exist because we have a passion to see you healthy. Knowing that food is the
        primary determinant of health, our goal is to provide what you need to stay healthy - food, drink, counseling, health talks, <em>etc.</em>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-justify">
        We're not very far from you. Visit us today, and your health can only get better!
      </p>
    </div>
